public class InitializationStore<V extends org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFAbstractValue<V>,S extends InitializationStore<V,S>> extends org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFAbstractStore<V,S>
A store that extends CFAbstractStore and additionally tracks which fields of the 'self' reference have been initialized.
